snippet.title: EternAlgoRhythm Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
EternAlgoRhythm is a rhythm game with procedurally generated music and tracks. It is releasing on the 16th of August 2024!

If this seems interesting to you, there's a free demo you can check out!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2678290/EternAlgoRhythm/
